quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo …ďe doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óen, o wa…ói etirgal ngal ka doŇčngal neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotoo…óo eewnii: \"Ko onon yo setee…ďe, Ko on wuy…ďe"
  12,71,"∆Āe fewtiti e ma…ď…ďe …ďe wi'i: \"Ko hon…óum hatti…óon"
  12,72,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men hattike etirde laam…óo on. Hino woodani kala addu…óo ngal, doŇčngal ngelooba, ko min woni fawtii…óo …óum"
  12,73,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, gom…óii hi…óon anndi men araali bonnugol ka leydi, men laataaki kadi wuy…ďe"
  12,74,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko wonata njo…ďdi makko si tawii ko on fenoo…ďe"
  12,75,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Njo…ďdi makko: ko kala mo: […óum] tawaa ka doŇčngal mun, haray ko kanko [tigir] woni njo…ďdi mun. Ko wano non men yo…ďitirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fu…ó…óori doŇčle ma…ď…ďe …óen ado doŇčngal neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doŇčngal neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laam…óo on, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi. Me…óen …ďantana darajaaji on mo Men muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]"
  12,77,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Si o wujjii, haray neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii\". Yuusufu mari …óum ka wonkii makko, o fe√Ī√Īinanaali …ďe …óum. O maaki: \"Ko onon …ďuri bonnde nokku! Ko Alla …ďuri anndude ko sifoto…óon"
  12,78,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko an yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyu…óo oggos; ∆īettu gooto e amen lonto makko. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
